I got it working now.&#13;
&#13;
Fixed few typos:&#13;
&#13;
block_item/nivoslider.tp&#13;
&#13;
in line 38 "Double quote" is missing and replaced "nivoslider_embed" with&#13;
               "nivoslide_block_item"&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
and in block/nivoslider.tpl put this code:&#13;
 &lt;code&gt;&#13;
     {def $valid_nodes = $block.valid_nodes}&#13;
 &#13;
&lt;!-- BLOCK: START --&gt;&#13;
&#13;
{def $my_node=fetch( 'content', 'node', hash( 'node_id', 154 ) )}&#13;
{node_view_gui view='block_item' content_node=$my_node}&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
&lt;!-- BLOCK: END --&gt;&#13;
 &#13;
{undef $valid_nodes}   &#13;
 &lt;/code&gt;&#13;
&#13;
with known node ID so I could check if it will work.&#13;
It is grate and flexible that nivoslider could be added with easy to block in frontpage.&#13;
Thanks again Stefano for pointing me in right direction.&#13;
Best Regards&#13;
Peter&#13;
