      <title>New version aviable for download</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/nivoslider/forum/general/new_version_aviable_for_download</link>
      <description>Just release new version ( 0.3 ) of nivoslider extension for ez publish&#13;
&#13;
Here is the change log :&#13;
&#13;
- Update nivoslider script&#13;
- Update jquery script&#13;
- Add new full view for nivoslider class&#13;
- Add new box-item view for nivoslider class&#13;
- Add slideInRight effect to nivoslider class&#13;
- Add slideInLeft effect to nivoslider class&#13;
- Add Start Slide effect to nivoslider class&#13;
- Add option Random Start to nivoslider class&#13;
- Add option Random Start to nivoslider class&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
Since there are 2 new view for the nivoslider class i added also 2 new image size, so edit the image.ini.php and add the correct size which you want.&#13;
&#13;
If you find any problem just contact me here on forum ( on section Bugs and Problems please ) </description>
